           --> SC Simplified Chinese 发光 fā guāng TC Traditional Chinese 發光  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 发亮 fā guāng，fā liàng TC Traditional Chinese 發亮 
 -- The lantern burned all night long.
 -- 灯笼彻夜都在发光。
 
