           --> SC Simplified Chinese 发热 fā rè TC Traditional Chinese 發熱  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 发烫 fā rè，fā tàng 
 -- The hot coals continue to burn after the fire goes out.
 -- 即使火已经熄灭，滚烫的煤块还是会继续发热。
 
burn vi (cause a stinging sensation)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 有酸痛感 yǒu suān tòng gǎn  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 有刺痛感 yǒu suān tòng gǎn，yǒu cì tòng gǎn 
 -- His arms burned after lifting weights for an hour.
 -- 举重几小时后，他的手臂酸痛不已。
 
burn vi (feel anger)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 感到生气 gǎn dào shēng qì TC Traditional Chinese 感到生氣  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 愤怒 gǎn dào shēng qì，fèn nù TC Traditional Chinese 憤怒 
 -- He was still burning about the subject two weeks later.
 -- 两周后，他还为那件事感到生气。
 
burn vi (become overcooked)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 烤焦 kǎo jiāo  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 烧糊 kǎo jiāo，shāo hù 
 -- Remember to take the chicken off the stove; don't let it burn this time!
 -- 记得把鸡从炉子上拿下来，这次别又烧焦了！
 
burn vi slang, figurative (be executed)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 被电刑处决，被烧死 bèi diàn xíng chǔ jué，bèi shāo sǐ  (俚语，比喻)
 -- I want to see that criminal burn!
 -- 我想亲眼看到那个犯人被处死！
 
