 -- 小心点！别在沙滩上晒伤了，不然你就不能下水了。
 
burn [sth] # vtr (combust fuel)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 使用…作为燃料 shǐ yòng zuò wéi rán liào  
 -- The plane must have burned a thousand litres by now.
 
