           --> SC Simplified Chinese 让…生气 ràng shēng qì TC Traditional Chinese 讓…生氣  
 -- The thought that John is dating his ex-girlfriend really burns him.
 
burn [sb/sth] # vtr US, slang (sports: beat, score against)
